{"tid":2193860,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人電腦MIC收音好那細聲","createTime":"2020-09-08T07:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T05:57:58.000Z","uid":139215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21ac60789720662bf646e412c08d3eb612fd26c1","tid":2193860,"uid":139215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"插3.5細聲<br />\n插USB又細聲<br />\n以為支MIC有問題 20 50 100 而家支咪1000蚊都係咁細聲 差D要放入個口到先有聲<br />\n係WIN10問題 定係 底板問題呢 定係間房大細 同個喇叭遠近又有無關係呢<br />\n上個DISCORD 我一個人講野人地已經要留心聽先聽到內容<br />\n兩個人講野 我加把口 基本上無人知道我講緊野<br />\n<br />\nGOOGLE教個D ON99 右鍵內容推高30試過晒無用<br />\n上網DL個D調音器 推高少少就拆晒聲 <br />\n有無人試過咁樣樣既問題 <br />\n有無大佬解救下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b230e9ec6ab4edb2dc8547fcddafc2f5759cb10c","tid":2193860,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"搵第二部電腦試咪知係咪電腦問題"},{"pid":"3034cbc29c9b3c2a3c546ea7ae4d53d1363be663","tid":2193860,"uid":139215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b230e9ec6ab4edb2dc8547fcddafc2f5759cb10c","tid":2193860,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"搵第二部電腦試咪知係咪電腦問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"已知 5支咪都無問題"},{"pid":"82e47de03b4377e123ae836395a237f358c620bb","tid":2193860,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3034cbc29c9b3c2a3c546ea7ae4d53d1363be663","tid":2193860,"uid":139215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b230e9ec6ab4edb2dc8547fcddafc2f5759cb10c","tid":2193860,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"搵第二部電腦試咪知係咪電腦問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"已知 5支咪都無問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"咁即係電腦setting問題/硬件問題<br />\n有冇試過用skype呢啲？ 有冇同樣問題"},{"pid":"78b4d92a470c8b884a7cfc1c884efc8e5c5f41da","tid":2193860,"uid":41330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi